What a Show… What a Moment!

The Main Stage at Beauty & Spa 2025 was LIT with the unstoppable @naseem_salon_academy – the GOAT of hair artistry!

History was made as @proads_india showcased India’s First-Ever Biotin Hair Color Inspirations, created LIVE by the master himself Mr. Naseem Salmani.

The crowd went wild, the stage glittered, and the colors spoke for themselves!

Catch the Snippets Now and relive the PRIME TIME SHOWSTOPPER that left everyone clapping without asking!

Thank you @naseem_salon_academy for making this moment unforgettable with PROADS at #BeautyAndSpaExpo.
